---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="parcelLab Named to CB Insights' Retail Tech 100 - parcelLab"
  description="parcelLab has been selected for CB Insights' inaugural Retail Tech 100 ranking, identifying the 100 most promising B2B eCommerce companies globally."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Company News</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab Named to CB Insights' Retail Tech 100</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">parcelLab Team</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2021-02-06">February 6, 2021</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>3 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          parcelLab has been selected for CB Insights' inaugural Retail Tech 100 ranking, which identifies the 100 most promising B2B eCommerce companies globally. The list encompasses startups from 21 countries working to transform customer experiences across the sales-to-delivery spectrum.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Notable Achievement</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">parcelLab represents one of only two German organizations included on the CB Insights Retail Tech 100 ranking.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">A Pivotal Moment for E-Commerce</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Tobias Buxhoidt, CEO of parcelLab, reflected on the recognition: "This year, e-commerce has changed dramatically. We've seen tremendous year-over-year growth and it's clear that online retail is here to stay."
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          He emphasized that parcelLab enables retailers to communicate directly with customers about shipping and returns, noting that engagement rates for their communications increased significantly during this period due to customers' heightened demand for delivery updates.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">The Retail Tech 100 by the Numbers</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">$14B+</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">total equity funding raised by participating companies</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">$4.7B</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">raised by companies in 2020 alone</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">19</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">unicorn-status companies on the list</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#3D3AD3]">21</span>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">countries represented across the ranking</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">Geographic Distribution</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          The Retail Tech 100 reflects the global nature of e-commerce innovation:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">North America:</strong> 59% (US leads with 55 companies)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Asia:</strong> 21%</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Europe:</strong> 16%</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#035740" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]"><strong class="text-[var(--ink)]">Latin America:</strong> 4%</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab's inclusion on the Retail Tech 100 reflects the company's mission of providing customizable post-purchase communication platforms. Partnering with 500+ global brands and 150+ carriers worldwide, parcelLab continues to help retailers own their customer relationships from checkout to delivery and beyond.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
